title: Kurt Seligmann Exotic Garden Shawl
description:
Shawl developed from Kurt Seligmann’s Exotic garden, 1954, from the collection of the Art Institute of Chicago.

Strange and wonderful botanical images abound in this opulent silk shawl.  The rich color palette makes this singular vision of nature always appropriate.

  • Dimension: 26 x 69 in.
  • Material: Silk
  • Dry Clean Only.
